{"type":"message","id":"76ed5c1f","parentId":"440a02b2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:13:27.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, there's a bug in the original code. `higher_low_count_10` should be counting when the low makes higher lows, not when the close makes higher lows. Let me look at the original code more carefully.\n\nThe original code had:\n```python\nhl = sum(1 for i in range(1, n-1) if closes[i] < closes[i-1] and closes[i] < closes[i+1])\n```\n\nThis counts local minima in closes, which is wrong. `higher_low` means the low price is higher than the previous low, so the bar is: higher low = low[i] > low[i-1] (when in an uptrend).\n\n\nAnd `lower_high` means the high price is lower than the previous high: high[i] < high[i-1].\n\nSo the correct definitions are:\n- Higher high count: highs[i] > max(highs[max(0, i-5):i]) \n- Higher low count: lows[i] > max(lows[max(0, i-5):i]) -- this checks if current low is higher than the max of previous lows... that's wrong for \"higher low\"\n- Lower high count: highs[i] < min(highs[max(0, i-5):i])\n\nActually, \"higher low\" means the current low is higher than the previous low, so it should be: lows[i] > max(lows[:i]) -- higher than ALL previous lows. For a strict definition: lows[i] > max(lows[max(0, i-window):i]).\n- \"Lower high\" means the current high is lower than the previous high: highs[i] < min(highs[max(0, i-window):i]).\n\nLet me fix this more carefully. The current edit has issues.","thinkingSignature":"0bf53ec86f58d6a93c9ff522c6ccf79e4d407a83ac2415258fd46b3c8a77bf00"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8ofcafg3cz0t_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/al_brooks_a_share_state_labeler.py","oldText":"    # --- 趋势结构组 ---\n    # 简化版：最近10根中，HH=收盘创前高新高次数，HL=收盘创前低新低次数\n    window = min(10, n - 1)\n    hh = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if highs[i] > max(highs[max(0, i-5):i]))\n    ll = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if lows[i] < min(lows[max(0, i-5):i]))\n    # LH/LL 用作下降趋势确认\n    lh = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if highs[i] < min(highs[max(0, i-5):i]))\n    hl = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if lows[i]  > max(lows[max(0, i-5):i]))\n    higher_high_count_10  = hh\n    higher_low_count_10   = hl\n    lower_high_count_10   = lh\n    lower_low_count_10    = ll","newText":"    # --- 趋势结构组 ---\n    # HH = 创前期新高次数，HL = 创前期新低次数（顺势结构计数）\n    # LH = 创前期新低次数（逆势结构），LL = 创前期新低次数（下降结构）\n    window = min(10, n - 1)\n    hh = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if highs[i] > max(highs[max(0, i-1):i]))\n    hl = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if lows[i] > max(lows[max(0, i-1):i]))\n    lh = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if highs[i] < min(highs[max(0, i-1):i]))\n    ll = sum(1 for i in range(n-window, n)\n             if lows[i] < min(lows[max(0, i-1):i]))\n    higher_high_count_10  = hh\n    higher_low_count_10   = hl\n    lower_high_count_10   = lh\n    lower_low_count_10    = ll"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18881,"output":936,"cacheRead":22332,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42149,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774573984108,"responseId":"06150ca0639211f17bfc8ed0893e7fcc"}}
