{"type":"message","id":"97fcc81d","parentId":"d5aef496","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:56:06.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I know exactly where to insert the fix. After line 435 (market_breadth, halt_reasons, gate_reasons are set), I'll add a block that updates `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` with the computed halt state.\n\nThe key insight: When `runtime_snapshot.authoritative` is True, the strategy report uses runtime state values for mode/risk_off/hard_stop. But for `halt_new_buy` and `risk_mode`, it ALWAYS computes from `profile_stats` (line 432). So the strategy report's halt can be DIFFERENT from runtime_risk_state's halt. The fix: after computing halt_new_buy, write it back to `runtime_risk_state_latest.json`.","thinkingSignature":"e666bbf7991c46524e94afff1502f18ca825cafc6a416a5c85667d32c1f6e145"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fgsj99zp99n4_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py","old_string":"        gate_reasons = unique_ordered(\n            [\n                bit.strip()\n                for stats in profile_stats\n                for bit in str(stats.get(\"gate_reasons\") or \"\").split(\"|\")\n                if bit.strip()\n            ]\n        )\n\n    buy_count = len([row for row in deduped_rows if str(row.get(\"action\") or \"\").upper() == \"BUY\"])","new_string":"        gate_reasons = unique_ordered(\n            [\n                bit.strip()\n                for stats in profile_stats\n                for bit in str(stats.get(\"gate_reasons\") or \"\").split(\"|\")\n                if bit.strip()\n            ]\n        )\n\n    # ── P1-001 修复：同步 computed halt state 回 runtime_risk_state_latest.json ──\n    # 防止 runtime_risk_state（event_watch 唯一真源）与 strategy_report 解同步\n    # 导致 runtime=normal / report=halt / event_watch=halt 三方矛盾\n    try:\n        rs_path = runtime_state_latest_path\n        if rs_path.exists():\n            rs = json.loads(rs_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n            if rs.get(\"latest_runtime\") is None:\n                rs[\"latest_runtime\"] = {}\n            rs[\"latest_runtime\"][\"mode\"] = risk_mode\n            rs[\"latest_runtime\"][\"halt_new_buy\"] = halt_new_buy\n            rs[\"latest_runtime\"][\"halt_reason\"] = halt_reasons[0] if halt_reasons else None\n            rs[\"latest_runtime\"][\"gate_reasons\"] = gate_reasons\n            rs[\"latest_runtime\"][\"market_breadth\"] = market_breadth\n            rs[\"generated_at\"] = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n            atomic_write_json(rs_path, rs)\n    except Exception:\n        pass  # 非关键路径，不阻断报告生成\n\n    buy_count = len([row for row in deduped_rows if str(row.get(\"action\") or \"\").upper() == \"BUY\"])"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51550,"output":639,"cacheRead":23032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75221,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774583751382,"responseId":"061532c7c91d8bfdecb28475435a37f0"}}
