correctly sets `source=paper_profiles` with `halt_new_buy=True`. This suggests the org module is intentionally using yesterday's data as the authoritative source when today's runtime state is unavailable. My previous test with `date_tag='20260327'` showed the condition should pass with the proper runtime state, but the actual execution is using a different `date_tag` value that triggers the fallback path instead.\n\nThe real problem is that `apply_runtime_overlay` prioritizes the org module's `paper_date_tag` (yesterday) over the runtime state's `date_tag` (today), so when they mismatch, it falls back to stale data. I need to fix this by having the overlay function prefer today's runtime state when it exists, rather than deferring to yesterday's paper data. The core issue is that `runtime_risk_state_latest` gets updated when the strategy report runs, but `event_watch` still reads yesterday's stale data. I need to fix `apply_runtime_overlay` to prioritize the runtime state file when its date_tag matches today, rather than defaulting to the paper execution summary's date. This way the event watch will pick up the fresh runtime state instead of being blocked by mismatched dates. The fallback to the report object is creating the inconsistency—the runtime state file is actually more authoritative than the report for today's data. I should restructure the logic to check the runtime state first when it's current, only falling back to the report object if the runtime state is stale or missing.","thinkingSignature":"31d8141557c38dc87e4861c6fb1c10f4a1f16fa877fc6dea027f2696072e7d79"},{"type":"text","text":"Found the root cause. `apply_runtime_overlay` uses `summary[\"paper_date_tag\"]` (= yesterday `20260326`) as the `date_tag`, causing runtime state's `date_tag=20260327` check to fail and fall back to stale paper data. Fix: prioritize runtime state's date when it's today:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n9ejv0sogsdv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":71,"limit":65,"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66662,"output":846,"cacheRead":23032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774584092144,"responseId":"0615341cc8c86033148bb41eb12351f4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b3b1c942","parentId":"1eeba307","timestamp":"2026-03-27T04:01:54.516Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n9ejv0sogsdv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\ndef apply_runtime_overlay(summary: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    date_tag = str(summary.get(\"strategy_report_date_tag\") or summary.get(\"paper_date_tag\") or datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n    runtime_obj, report_obj = load_runtime_overlay(date_tag)\n    latest_runtime = runtime_obj.get(\"latest_runtime\") or {}\n\n    if str(runtime_obj.get(\"date_tag\") or \"\") == date_tag and latest_runtime:\n        summary[\"risk_off\"] = bool(latest_runtime.get(\"risk_off\"))\n        pe = dict(summary.get(\"paper_execution_status\") or {})\n        pe.update(\n            {\n                \"source\": \"runtime_risk_state_latest\",\n                \"mode\": latest_runtime.get(\"mode\"),\n                \"risk_off\": latest_runtime.get(\"risk_off\"),\n                \"hard_stop\": latest_runtime.get(\"hard_stop\"),\n                \"halt_new_buy\": latest_runtime.get(\"halt_new_buy\"),\n                \"halt_reason\": latest_runtime.get(\"halt_reason\"),\n                \"market_breadth\": latest_runtime.get(\"market_breadth\"),\n                \"gate_reasons\": latest_runtime.get(\"gate_reasons\") or [],\n                \"allowed_to_open_new_positions\": not bool(latest_runtime.get(\"halt_new_buy\")),\n                \"runtime_state_path\": str(RUNTIME_STATE_LATEST),\n            }\n        )\n        summary[\"paper_execution_status\"] = pe\n        source_paths = dict(summary.get(\"source_paths\") or {})\n        source_paths[\"runtime_risk_state_json\"] = str(RUNTIME_STATE_LATEST)\n        summary[\"source_paths\"] = source_paths\n\n    # 注意：第二个 overlay 块不得覆盖第一个 runtime_risk_state 块已设置的字段，\n    # 因为 runtime_risk_state 含有盘中实时门控，比 morning strategy report 更新鲜。\n    # 只在 runtime_risk_state 无数据时才用 strategy_report 的值做 fallback。\n    trade_date_text = str(report_obj.get(\"trade_date\") or \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\")\n    if trade_date_text == date_tag and report_obj and not latest_runtime:\n        pe = dict(summary.get(\"paper_execution_status\") or {})\n        pe.setdefault(\"source\", \"strategy_report\")\n        if report_obj.get(\"risk_mode\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"mode\", report_obj.get(\"risk_mode\"))\n        if report_obj.get(\"risk_off\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"risk_off\", report_obj.get(\"risk_off\"))\n            summary.setdefault(\"risk_off\", bool(report_obj.get(\"risk_off\")))\n        if report_obj.get(\"hard_stop\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"hard_stop\", report_obj.get(\"hard_stop\"))\n        if report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\") is not None:\n            pe.setdefault(\"halt_new_buy\", report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\"))\n            pe.setdefault(\"allowed_to_open_new_positions\", not bool(report_obj.get(\"halt_new_buy\")))\n        if report_obj.get(\"trigger_reason\"):\n            pe.setdefault(\"halt_reason\", report_obj.get(\"trigger_reason\"))\n        if \"market_breadth\" in report_obj:\n            pe.setdefault(\"market_breadth\", report_obj.get(\"market_breadth\"))\n        summary[\"paper_execution_status\"] = pe\n    return summary\n\n\ndef should_reset_baseline(prev: dict[str, Any] | None, cur: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[bool, str]:\n    if not prev:\n        return False, \"\"\n\n    prev_dt = parse_dt(prev.get(\"generated_at\"))\n    if prev_dt != datetime.min and (datetime.now() - prev_dt).days >= 2:\n        return True, \"previous_state_stale\"\n\n    prev_source_paths = prev.get(\"source_paths\", {}) or {}\n    old_holdings = str(prev_source_paths.get(\"app_holdings_csv\") or \"\")\n    old_live_report = str(prev_source_paths.get(\"live_system_report\") or \"\")\n    if \"ths_app_holdings_\" in old_holdings or \"live_system_v1\" in old_live_report:\n\n[165 more lines in file. Use offset=136 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774584114505}}
{"type":"message","id":"27c4d6c2","parentId":"b3b1c942","timestamp":"2026-03-27T04:02:05.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the issue clearly. The condition at line 77 checks:\n```python\nif str(runtime_obj.get(\"date_tag\") or \"\") == date_tag and latest_runtime:\n```\n\nWhere `date_tag = \"20260326\"` (from `summary[\"paper_date_tag\"]`) and `runtime_obj.get(\"date_tag\") = \"20260327\"`. So the condition is False.\n\nThe fix: when `runtime_obj` has today's date_tag, we should use it regardless of `summary[\"paper_date_tag\"]`. I'll restructure the logic to:\n1. First check if runtime_obj has today's date_tag and use it\n2. Then fall back to the existing logic\n\nHere's the fix:","thinkingSignature":"2eb2d5f24e0df790d1ea0799676c4923fb0e648ea247e8c0f6bc7d45af2c027a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qvnxmcnkob4j_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py","old_string":"def apply_runtime_overlay(summary: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    date_tag = str(summary.get(\"strategy_report_date_tag\") or summary.get(\"paper_date_tag\") or datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n    runtime_obj, report_obj = load_runtime_overlay(date_tag)\n    latest_runtime = runtime_obj.get(\"latest_runtime\") or {}\n\n    if str(runtime_obj.get(\"date_tag\") or \"\") == date_tag and latest_runtime:","new_string":"def apply_runtime_overlay(summary: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    date_tag = str(summary.get(\"strategy_report_date_tag\") or summary.get(\"paper_date_tag\") or datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n    today_tag = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    runtime_obj, report_obj = load_runtime_overlay(date_tag)\n    latest_runtime = runtime_obj.get(\"latest_runtime\") or {}\n\n    # P1-001 修复：优先用 runtime_risk_state_latest 当日数据，忽略 paper_date_tag 的历史偏移\n    # runtime_risk_state_latest.json 由 strategy_report 在每次运行后同步更新，\n    # 其 date_tag 