{"type":"message","id":"fdd20953","parentId":"09c2f01d","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:19:03.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"But wait - the issue here is actually the OPPOSITE direction now. The runtime (from `runtime_risk_state_latest.json`) says halt=True, while the report says normal/False. This means the `generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py` at 11:35 computed `halt=False` and wrote it to the dated file, but `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` was updated later by the close bundle to halt=True.\n\nSo the TRUE root cause is that:1. `generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py` writes `risk_mode=normal, halt=False` to both dated and latest files (at 11:35)\n2. P1-001 fix #1 syncs halt back to `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` - but this means the 11:35 report's halt=False was synced back, so runtime also became False at that point\n\n\n3. The close bundle at 15:20 updated `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` to halt=True, and also overwrote the latest report file with halt=True, but left the dated file untouched at its original 11:35 timestamp with halt=False\n4. Now `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` shows halt=True while the dated report still shows halt=False\n\nThis reveals the second-order effect of my P1-001 fix: by having the report sync its computed halt state back to runtime, any subsequent updates to runtime (like what the close bundle does at 15:20) create this divergence where the dated report becomes stale relative to the updated runtime state.\n\nThe core issue is that `generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py` only writes to the latest file, not the dated one, so after 15:20 the latest report and runtime both reflect halt=True while the dated report remains stuck at halt=False. Rather than trying to patch the dated file retroactively, I should just ensure the audit and tester tools always read from the latest file instead, which is what my timestamp-based fix accomplishes.","thinkingSignature":"2c2284f5a7b6ae25af54089f5f7c3e39465936edd20bf3cdcb9ac7fe9e046fbf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8krntkf33o2b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -m py_compile scripts/run_quant_p0_audit.py && echo \"语法OK\" && cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace && python3 scripts/run_quant_p0_audit.py 2>&1 | tail -8","yieldMs":25000,"timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69456,"output":508,"cacheRead":23032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92996,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774606732452,"responseId":"06158c8c97f1d694f67cda9b78e9fda1"}}
